Loved this salad! Made completely according to recipe and turned out great. Read some other reviewers who had trouble finding citrus dressing. Litehouse does a tangy citrus dressing (which also has some heat) which I found with the refrigerated dressings in the vegetable isle. Good Stuff!!!!!!

